A simple tool/script to collect swap related information.
Usage:
	make
	./fiostat.sh -o xxx

Some options for fiostat.sh:
-l	lock memory. In swap, application data/code segment can be reclaimed, this
	makes sure these not happen.
-d	delay time for each simpling.
-c	simpling times. If this option isn't enabled, the tool will simpling
	forever till it's killed.
-o	output directory.
